{"id":232966667,"title":"[APOD] 蒸發中的丘澤彗星","content":"https://i.imgur.com/064IhNi.jpg\n說明: \n\n彗尾從何而來？\n\n在彗核上，最後形成彗尾的噴流，其實並不會源自特定的位置。\n\n彗星噴流的最佳影像之一，可參見2014年到2016年間繞行丘澤彗星（Comet CG）的歐洲航天局．羅塞塔太空船，攝於2015年的這幅主題影像。\n\n這張影像證實，隨著丘澤彗星靠近太陽受熱，羽狀的氣體塵埃從難以數計的位置冒出來。\n\n這顆彗星有二個明顯分瓣，大者寬度約4公里，較小者寬約2.5公里，二者以一道細頸相連。\n\n分析指出這種蒸發發生在彗星表面下的深處，最後才以塵埃和冰噴流的形式穿出表面。\n\n丘澤彗星（亦稱為67P彗星）在周期6.44年的繞日軌道中，半徑大約會縮減1公尺，依這個損耗率來推算，這顆彗星在數千年內就會完全銷毀。\n\n在2016年，羅塞塔太空船以受控撞擊丘澤彗星表面的方式，終結其任務。","excerpt":"說明：彗尾從何而來？在彗核上，最後形成彗尾的噴流，其實並不會源自特定的位置。彗星噴流的最佳影像之一，可參見2014年到2016年間繞行丘澤彗星（Comet CG）的歐洲航天局．羅塞塔太空船，攝於201","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":false,"pinned":false,"forumId":"e33fd5d2-025f-46e4-8b81-3f6fecdd25e1","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2020-01-27T11:00:39.124Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-27T11:00:39.124Z","commentCount":0,"likeCount":1,"tags":[],"topics":["APOD","每日一天文圖"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":false,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"廢文","forumAlias":"whysoserious","school":"國立清華大學","department":"資訊工程學系","replyTitle":null,"gender":"M","personaSubscriptable":null,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":1}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/064IhNi.jpg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"a454e3e2-b46f-4eee-988e-05b35e1ed21d","url":"https://i.imgur.com/064IhNil.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://i.imgur.com/064IhNil.jpg","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/064IhNil.jpg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2020-01-27T11:00:39.124Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-27T11:00:39.124Z"},{"id":"a454e3e2-b46f-4eee-988e-05b35e1ed21d","url":"https://i.imgur.com/064IhNi.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://imgur.com/064IhNi","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/064IhNil.jpg","type":"image/imgur","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2020-01-27T11:00:39.124Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-27T11:00:39.124Z"}],"postAvatar":""}